Fiji was featured prominently in the Nature Methods review on [http://www.nature.com/nmeth/journal/v7/n3s/full/nmeth.1431.html Visualization of image data from cells to organisms]. The review is one of a series of articles accompanying the conference Visualizing Biological Data (VizBi) held at EMBL Heidelberg March 3-5. The reviews are available free of charge as [http://www.nature.com/nmeth/journal/v7/n3s/index.html supplement] from Nature Methods web site.
